html
  head
    meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    link(rel="stylesheet" href="style.css")
    title Game Rules
  body
    .container 
      main.rules-box
          h1 Loop Quest
          h2 Game Rules
          p Read the instructions before starting the game.

          h3 How to Play
          ul
            li Roll the dice.
            li Move your token on the game board.
            li If you land on a QR tile, scan the QR code.
            li Answer the Python loop question.
            li If your answer is wrong, skip your next turn.
            li If your answer is correct, continue playing.

          h3 Scoring
          .scoring-formula
            p Final score is calculated based on:
            p Correct Answers / Total Attempts × 100%

          h3 Winning Condition
          p The player with the highest score wins.
          a.submit-btn(href="/leaderboard") View Leaderboard
          p.return-message Return to the physical board to begin the game.